entry.def: If there is a predominance of one type of person or thing, there are many more of that type than of any other type.

example.ex: Another interesting note was the predominance of London club players.
example.tran: 另一个有趣的现象是，伦敦俱乐部的球员在数量上占优势。

entry.def: If someone or something has pre- dominance, they have the most power or importance among a group of people or things.

example.ex: Eventually even their economic predominance was to suffer.
example.tran: 甚至最终，连他们在经济上的主导地位也会受损。
